    <item>
      <title>联合健康首席执行官向国会辩护网络攻击反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/unitedhealth-ceo-defends-cyberattack-response-to-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合健康集团 (UnitedHealth Group Inc.) 首席执行官安德鲁·威蒂 (Andrew Witty) 在华盛顿举行的首场背靠背听证会上，为该公司对灾难性网络攻击的应对措施进行了辩护，这场网络攻击导致医生的付款中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/unitedhealth-ceo-defends-cyberattack-response-to-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:31:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软将负责任人工智能团队从 350 人增至 400 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/microsoft-boosts-responsible-ai-team-from-350-to-400-personnel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司扩大了负责确保其人工智能产品安全的团队，去年人员数量从 350 人增加到 400 人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/microsoft-boosts-responsible-ai-team-from-350-to-400-personnel</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 13:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
