    <item>
      <title>马斯克削弱了特斯拉充电器的价格，拜登称赞这是“一件大事”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/musk-undercuts-tesla-chargers-biden-had-lauded-as-a-big-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)推翻了白宫去年初向其他汽车制造商开放特斯拉电动汽车充电器的协议，对乔·拜登(JoeBiden)总统的电动汽车议程造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/musk-undercuts-tesla-chargers-biden-had-lauded-as-a-big-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:47:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管大型科技公司不断支出，人工智能硬件股票仍遭受重创</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ai-hardware-stocks-get-pummeled-even-as-big-tech-keeps-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于半导体和其他人工智能计算硬件制造商来说，好消息是：科技巨头计划继续投入巨资。坏消息是投资者在本财报季更难给人留下深刻印象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/ai-hardware-stocks-get-pummeled-even-as-big-tech-keeps-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉解散超级充电团队，冲击​​更广阔的电动汽车市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/tesla-axes-supercharger-team-in-blow-to-other-automakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司几乎取消了整个超级充电站组织，该组织已经建立了庞大的公共充电站网络，美国几乎所有主要汽车制造商都在利用该网络。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/tesla-axes-supercharger-team-in-blow-to-other-automakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:46:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊因人工智能需求实现年度最大云销售增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amazon-reports-strong-cloud-unit-sales-on-rising-ai-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司的云部门实现了一年来最强劲的销售增长，这表明随着企业恢复在包括人工智能服务在内的技术项目上的支出，该零售商最赚钱的部门正在从低迷中复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/amazon-reports-strong-cloud-unit-sales-on-rising-ai-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:12:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超微因未能满足市场的高期望而步履蹒跚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/super-micro-gives-sunny-sales-outlook-fueling-ai-enthusiasm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超微电脑公司(Super Micro Computer Inc.)公布的季度销售额略低于预期，周三开盘后股价暴跌。结果令投资者感到失望，他们对这家服务器制造商的业务将受益于人工智能相关的需求抱有极高的期望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/super-micro-gives-sunny-sales-outlook-fueling-ai-enthusiasm</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:11:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pinterest 营收创六个月新高，购物业务强劲增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinterest-revenue-surges-on-popularity-of-shopping-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pinterest Inc. 公布第一季度销售额和用户增长超出华尔街预期，这得益于对购物的推动和对 Z 世代用户的关注，该公司在六个月内涨幅最大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pinterest-revenue-surges-on-popularity-of-shopping-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:07:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
